data.description: Convenient Greer location in highly sought-after neighborhood of Shelburne Farms. Well-maintained 3 bedroom/2 bathroom home with bonus room plus sun room. Spacious open living area and kitchen floor plan with cathedral ceilings. Kitchen includes breakfast nook and new range. Beyond the kitchen is a true gem, the sun room. This room displays tons of natural light with its floor to ceiling windows. The great room has fireplace with gas logs. New carpet throughout. Separate dining room. All bedrooms on the main level. The master boasts a large walk-in closet, separate garden tub and walk-in shower. Additional living space and lots of walk-out attic storage in the 2nd floor bonus room. Outside features composite fencing and decking. Immaculately kept crawlspace. Offers many community amenities-pool, pond, walking trails and playground. If buyer's decision to purchase is based on numerical representations, the buyer or buyer's agent is responsible for verifying all information.
